{"tid":599379,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB 劇集宇宙劇本，有無高手接力?","createTime":"2018-03-20T11:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T04:37:37.000Z","uid":1910,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3acc7f537af334c6b0b99a4fb86ba7d45d3589f2","tid":599379,"uid":1910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:00:32.000Z","msg":"2023年，唐立言(郭晉安飾)因在獄中表現良好，獲提早出獄。出獄後，立言向張承希(鄭嘉穎飾)坦承認錯，承希亦放下了與立言的恩怨。不久，立言得悉承希成為了一名律師，名為LAW霸，為民請命。眼見承希深受街坊歡迎，而自己則受盡眾人白眼，立言心中的恨意再度燃燒起來。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9wxlmt0g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9wxlmt0g&h=02692879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2bdvn1j4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2bdvn1j4&h=82268f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為求報仇，立言在一宗交通意外的案件中向承希的對頭律師韋國涵(林韋辰飾)洩露承希所得的證據，令承希的當事人馬季(馬國明飾) 無辜入獄。為求上訴，承希與文申俠(王浩信飾)合作，打算為馬季討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nxwadzo9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnxwadzo9&h=d858657b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4p0v6n7j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4p0v6n7j&h=60c56a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n申俠在調查的過程中，發現立言的舉動有可疑，正打算拆穿其真面目之際，竟收到立言遇到交通意外的消息，趕到醫院後，發現立言因頭部受到撞擊，變成傻人，不但認不出眾人，更表示自己名叫丁常旺。申俠覺得事有可疑，但苦無證據下只得暫時作罷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jry04g3u\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjry04g3u&h=9e519347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在醫院中，立言認識了在交換身份後產下兒子的鄺港生(陳豪飾)。立言在無意中聽到鄺港生與宋仲基(歐陽震華飾)的對話，得悉時空的士的秘密，於是偷偷離開醫院前往新光戲院取得功能卡。穿越時空的過程中，立言發現自了己當年犯罪的漏洞，卻苦於無法改變過去，只能眼白白看見自己鋃鐺入獄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6o5fhnw9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6o5fhnw9&h=2a8117a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gdpnxhi7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgdpnxhi7&h=a2399244&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不久，立言被醫院判定為精神失常，需要入住精神病康復中心。在康復中心中，立言認識了烏博士(廖啟智飾)，博士堅拒承認自己患病，更表示自己研究出時空旅行的秘密。為改變過去，立言孤注一擲，跟隨博士進行時空實驗。結果，立言成功回到了過去，卻在準備修改過去前被傳回現實。原來博士要求立言先到秦代把項少龍(古天樂飾)及嬴政(林峰飾)二人帶回現代，才答應為立言進行時空穿梭，立言無可選擇之下，只好踏上前往秦國之旅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rowgqbh7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frowgqbh7&h=f73538dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5swridq3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5swridq3&h=61753988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時連接咗與敵同行，怒火街頭，降魔的，踩過界，阿旺新傳，誇世代同尋秦記，有無高手接力? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513e1628816d468797567e83b285e2cca4ecd46f","tid":599379,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b802603d411758ec67b74ae45ae5bec04f23caf6","tid":599379,"uid":1910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T12:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a9fc049685fd77d04a1626aad1a90524cf4f2a","tid":599379,"uid":82905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T14:30:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5456e8bf61a10fd7838d5c51ae25a0a0231bca5a","tid":599379,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T22:25:51.000Z","msg":"Gd"},{"pid":"28656e85db990c8fe8a1299635a22d16a53baeb7","tid":5